<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 服务器错误 - Affirm后台管理</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center; padding: 80px 20px;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 6rem; margin: 0; color: #e74c3c;">500</h1>
        <h2>服务器内部错误</h2>
        <p>请求处理过程中发生了错误，请稍后重试或联系管理员。</p>
        <% if (process.env.NODE_ENV !== 'production' && error) { %>
        <pre style="text-align:left; background:#f8f8f8; padding:16px; border-radius:4px; overflow:auto; margin-top:20px;"><%= error %></pre>
        <% } %>
        <a href="/admin" style="display:inline-block; margin-top:20px; padding:10px 24px; background:#3498db; color:#fff; border-radius:4px; text-decoration:none;">返回仪表板</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
